arStrings.szText: "Were you just possessed? Are you alright?"
Ugh, I think so... but more importantly, I now have the knowledge I sought. Thank you, spirit, for showing us the truth.
Dazed and recovering from being possessed, but grateful for learning what he did through the spirit's possession.
I've seen your suffering at the hands of the Zakarum - the intolerance, the violence. I'm sorry your family couldn't be saved. But maybe others still can.
Thank you both. I will take what I've learned here to the Cathedral of Light. I hope I'm not too late.
